This Short Film is made by Naati Factory initiating the new trend of promoting the Kannada movies. This film is to promote the New Kannada Film ‘Beautiful Manasugalu’.  Which is releasing on Jan 20th 2017. Lucia Fame ‘Sathish Neenasam’ and ‘Sruthi Hariharan’ coming together on the big screen after 3 years. 
This short film is the mixture of Lucia and Beautiful manasugalu movies added up with the Naati Humour style.  #naatifactory
